/**                                                                         **/
/**   mswindow.c                                                            **/
/**                                                                         **/
/**   This file contains the code to handle input from a window, via the    **/
/**   the keyboard, and output to a window. The file also contains code to  **/
/**   handle various Windows requests pertaining to an open Server window.  **/
